PersonalMission.Name: SPG-10: All Included
PersonalMission.Description: The battle situation can change rapidly—always keep an eye on the minimap and make sure you have a clear view of enemy vehicles. You will have to move across the map all the time instead of staying in one position. Your allies rely on your SPG firepower, so do your best in the right time and place.

Primary.Conditions: •  Cause, or assist in causing 2,000 HP of damage by stunning or immobilizing

Secondary.Conditions: •  Allies must destroy an enemy vehicle stunned or immobilized by you
